				<td colspan="2"><span><a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/item.aspx?item=11646">http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/item.aspx?item=11646</a>
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------
<br />
<b>Correction and fun facts
<br />
</b>------------------------------------------------------------
<br />
<b>Correction:</b>
<br />
The Amulet of Necropotence's level for effect is level 1 (not level 50 as listed on the site)
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------
<br />
<b>Fun Facts:</b>
<br />
-With levatate you can boost yourself up about 10 ft. which can help climb walls in rare cases.
<br />

<br />
-Only horse models need to be on while your skelly.
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------
<br />
<b>FAQ:</b>
<br />
Q: 'Why is the amulet of necropotence worth as much as it is?'
<br />
A: Sure it drops in an easy zone like Plane of Fear but the drop rate on it is close to a 1 in 30 chance of dropping.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
